File:POLAND world Volkswagen Passat.webp|Volkswagen Passat<ref>[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Volkswagen_Passat Volkswagen Passat] on Wikipedia.</ref> 1.9 TDI - a popular car model in Poland.
